# Gemini Protocol Document

## Introduction

The Gemini protocol is a new internet protocol which is heavier than Gopher but lighter than the web.

=> gemini://gemini.circumlunar.space/ Project Gemini Home

## Features

Gemini has the following features:

* Simple text format
* Privacy focused
* No client-side scripting
* No inline images

> The Gemini protocol is designed to be simple and private.

## Example Code

```python
import gemini

def fetch_page(url):
    response = gemini.request(url)
    return response.text
```

